---
title: Turkey and Cheddar Burgers with Roasted Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Tender ground turkey, gooey cheddar cheese and caramelized onions, what more could you want? An elegant side of roasted wedges served with a creamy green onion dipping sauce makes for a match made in heaven!
